title: Software Engineering Intern
description: Develop and maintain web applications using modern frameworks. Work on real projects with mentorship from senior engineers.

title: Data Science Intern
description: Analyze large datasets and build machine learning models. Collaborate with data scientists on predictive analytics projects.

title: Cloud Infrastructure Intern
description: Work on AWS cloud services and infrastructure automation. Learn about scalable systems and DevOps practices.

title: Full Stack Developer Intern
description: Develop end-to-end features for e-commerce platform. Experience with React, Node.js, and microservices architecture.

title: AI Research Intern
description: Research and implement cutting-edge AI algorithms. Work on natural language processing and computer vision projects.

title: Mobile App Developer Intern
description: Develop mobile applications for iOS and Android. Work on user experience and performance optimization.

title: FinTech Software Intern
description: Develop financial technology solutions and banking applications. Work on secure payment systems and digital banking features.

title: Backend Systems Intern
description: Design and implement scalable backend systems. Work with databases, APIs, and distributed systems.

title: Data Analytics Intern
description: Create dashboards and reports for business intelligence. Work with SQL, Python, and data visualization tools.

title: Cybersecurity Intern
description: Assess security vulnerabilities and implement security measures. Learn about penetration testing and security protocols.
